query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (rt.role like '%colin theys%' OR rt.role like '%Chris Kolaskos%' OR rt.role like '%IW%' OR rt.role like '%Hannah Nicholas%') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','cast','complete+verified') AND cn.name not like '%Legendary%' AND cn.country_code in ('gr','az','mg','hr','hu') AND t.production_year > 2005 AND t.production_year < 2009 AND mi.info in ('Kyrgyz','Gujarati','German','Inuktitut','Catalan','Hindi','Brazilian Sign Language','Filipino','Czech','Irish Gaelic','Slovenian') AND an.name not like '%d%' AND an.name not like '%O%' AND it3.info in ('quotes','LD disc size','screenplay-teleplay','height','LD year','gross','pictorial','LD analog right','birth date','LD original title','LD release date','budget','books','LD sharpness','novel','certificates','opening weekend','LD sound encoding','biographical movies') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','crew','cast') AND it.info in ('LD subtitles','novel','LD status of availablility','keywords','magazine cover photo','bottom 10 rank','countries','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','LD video quality','color info','portrayed in','biographical movies','languages','LD pressing plant','budget','trade mark','book') AND (pi.note like '%Steve Harrison%' OR pi.note like '%Adam Showtime Palmer%' OR pi.note like '%Be Free Films%')
